data.description: Investors - this ranch is nestled in the Preston Park neighborhood. It's a 3 bedroom, 1 bath home with an open layout and sits on a generous .20 acre lot. Outside, you will find a large, fully fenced backyard. This home also includes a detached 2-car garage. In close proximity to I-65, Fern Valley Rd, and Preston Hwy, you will have easy access to shopping and restaurants. Schedule a showing today! **This home is a short sale and all offers are subject to 3rd party approval. Bring us your BEST OFFER!*
